{
  "texts": [
    "The two questions were: \"Open question: What is, in your opinion, the first thing that needs to change in the sector?",
    "(Please provide 1 answer)\" (Q67), and \"Comments and suggestions that you could not include in the questions can be written below.\"",
    "The open comment boxes were present in each part: Part 2 (Q12), Part 3 (Q17), Part 4 (Q25, Q28, Q30), Part 5 (Q34, Q39), Part 6 (Q44), Part 7 (Q51, Q53), Part 8 (Q58, Q60, Q63), and Part 9 (Q67, Q68).",
    "For an overview of all questions, please refer to the Data availability section.",
    "The questionnaire was administered in September and October 2021, with invitations disseminated through the website www."
